    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Consider the Health Standpoint</strong>&mdash;The physical surroundings in the cities are often a peril to health. The constant liability to contact with disease, the prevalence of foul air, impure water, impure food, the crowded, dark, unhealthful dwellings, are some of the many evils to be met.",
