    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Hotbeds of Iniquity</strong>&mdash;The cities are filled with temptation. We should plan our work in such a way as to keep our young people as far as possible from this contamination.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">3<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"CL 30.1\" data-link=\"25.248\">Country Living, 30</span>.</span></a></sup>",
