    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The children and youth should be carefully guarded. They should be kept away from the hotbeds of iniquity that are to be found in our cities.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">4<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"CL 12.1\" data-link=\"25.85\">Ibid., 12</span>.</span></a></sup>",
