    "content": "<strong>Labor Troubles</strong>&mdash;Through the working of trusts and the results of labor unions and strikes, the conditions of life in the city are constantly becoming more and more difficult. Serious troubles are before us, and for many families removal from the cities will become a necessity.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">6<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MH 364.1\" data-link=\"135.1835\">The Ministry of Healing, 364</span>.</span></a></sup>",
