    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Oh, that God&apos;s people had a sense of the impending destruction of thousands of cities now almost given to idolatry!<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">8<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"RH 9-10-1903\" data-link=\"821.23295\">The Review and Herald, September 10, 1903</span>.</span></a></sup>",
