    "content": "<strong>For Worldly Interests and Love of Gain</strong>&mdash;It is often the case that parents are not careful to surround their children with right influences. In choosing a home, they think more of their worldly interests than of the moral and social atmosphere, and the children form associations that are unfavorable to the development of piety and the formation of right characters....",
