    "refcode_long": "The Adventist Home, p. 139.3 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Time Now to Move From the Cities</strong>&mdash;Take your families away from the cities is my message.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">16<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"CL 29.5\" data-link=\"25.245\">Ibid., 29</span>.</span></a></sup>",
