    "refcode_long": "The Adventist Home, p. 139.5 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Before the overflowing scourge shall come upon the dwellers of the earth, the Lord calls upon all who are Israelites indeed to prepare for that event. To parents He sends the warning cry: Gather your children into your own houses; gather them away from those who are disregarding the commandments of God, who are teaching and practicing evil. Get out of the large cities as fast as possible.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">18<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"6T 195.1\" data-link=\"118.1049\">Testimonies for the Church 6:195</span>.</span></a></sup>",
